48 "(c1) Notwithstanding subsection (c) of this section, a person required to submit to
49 satellite-based monitoring pursuant to G.S. 15A-1368.4(b1)(6) shall continue to participate in
50 satellite-based monitoring beyond the period of post-release supervision until the Commission
