6 EXCLUDE DEPARTMENT OF ADULT CORRECTION INVESTIGATIONS FROM
7 CERTAIN INFORMATION TECHNOLOGY RESTRICTIONS
8 SECTION 6.2.(a) G.S. 143-805(d) reads as rewritten:
