14 under the supervision of, the Department of Adult Correction or matters
15 related to the misuse of devices owned by the Department of Adult
16 Correction."
17 SECTION 6.2.(b) This section is effective when it becomes law and applies to
18 investigations occurring before, on, or after that date.
